- [ ] 2. Write the expand-phase migration script with additive schema changes only.
- [ ] 3. Implement the backfill as batched, checkpointed, idempotent steps with progress logging.
- [ ] 4. Add index builds using an online strategy where available, with lock and statement timeouts set.
- [ ] 5. Implement compatibility in the application (dual-write, tolerant reads, or a feature flag) for the rollout window.
- [ ] 6. Document every irreversible step with its point of no return and the manual recovery path for each.
